<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
    <style>
        .payment-form {
            font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif;
            margin: -15px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            padding-bottom: 0px;
            margin-right: 55px;
            margin-bottom: -35px;
            height: fit-content;
        }

        .Container {
            flex-direction: row;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            max-width: 800px;
            height: fit-content;
            margin: 0px auto;
            border-radius: 5px;
            display: flex;
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .clg-logo {
            max-width: 180px;
            max-height: 100%;
            border-right: 2px solid #000;
        }

        .image {
            height: 150px;
            width: 150px;
            margin-right: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .payment-form__header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .payment-form__title {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-top: 0px;
            margin-bottom: 0px;
            padding: 2px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif;
        }

        .payment-form__subtitle {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #020202;
            margin-top: 0px;
            margin-bottom: 0px;
            padding: 2px;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-family: "Tiro Devanagari Hindi", serif;
        }

        .payment-form__body {
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .payment-form__subject {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 0px;
            text-decoration-line: underline;
            margin-top: 0%;
        }

        .payment-form__paragraph {
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 0px;
            justify-content: space-between;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            max-width: 400px;
            margin-top: 0px;
            text-align: justify;
        }

        .payment-form__paragraph1 {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-top: 0px;
            text-align: justify;
        }

        .payment-form__paragraph2 {
            font-size: 17px;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-top: 0px;
            text-align: justify;
            font-weight: 400;
        }

        .payment-form__table {
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            margin-left: 30px;
        }

        .payment-form__table-header {
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }

        .payment-form__table-header-cell {
            padding: 5px;
            border: 1px solid #080808;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .payment-form__table-body {
            border: 1px solid #0c0c0c;
        }

        .payment-form__table-row {
            height: 40px;
        }

        .payment-form__table-cell {
            padding: 10px;
            border: 1px solid #050505;
            font-weight: 400;
            color: #000;
        }

        .payment-form__table-cell1 {
            padding: 10px;
            border: 1px solid #050505;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .payment-form__approval {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding-top: 20px;
            margin-top: 10px;
            padding-right: 20px;
            color: #000;
        }

        .payment-form__approval1 {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: flex-end;
            padding-right: 50px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            margin-top: 10px;
            color: #000;
        }

        .payment-form__approval-text {
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .payment-form__approval-sign {
            display: block;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .payment-form__approval-sign1 {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: flex-end;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .payment-form__approval-sign2 {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .payment-form__approval-name {
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-bottom: -20px;
        }

        .payment-form__approval-position {
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #000;
            margin-bottom: 0;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .ordered-list li {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            margin-left: 30px;
            text-align: justify;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class='Container'>
        <div class='clg-logo'>
            <img src="/CLG-LOGO.png" alt="Description of the image" class='image' />
        </div>
        <form class="payment-form">
            <div class="payment-form__header">
                <h3 class="payment-form__subtitle">राष्ट्रीय प्रौद्योगिकी संस्थान नागालैंड</h3>
                <h3 class="payment-form__title">NATIONAL INSTITUTE OF TECHNOLOGY NAGALAND</h3>
                <h3 class="payment-form__title">Chumukedima, Nagaland-797 103</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="payment-form__body">
                <h3 class="payment-form__subject">Submitted to Director</h3>
                <div class="payment-form__approval1">
                    <div>
                        <p class="payment-form__paragraph2">
                            NIT-N/ADMN/ACAD/2024/<%= orderData['month'] %>-<%= orderData['month-number'] %>/<%= orderData['year-number'] %>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <p class="payment-form__paragraph2">
                            Date: <%= orderData['today'] %>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>       
                <p class="payment-form__paragraph1">
                    Sub: NIT-N – Refund of Excess Registration Fee paid – Approval requested – regarding
                </p>
                <p class="payment-form__paragraph1">
                    Ref: 1. <%= orderData['Reference'] %>
                </p>
                <p class="payment-form__paragraph1">
                      The following undermentioned <%= orderData.course %> of <%= orderData.branch %> department, has submitted a request for refund for the payment of Excess Registration Fee paid from bank to Institute account  as <%= orderData['use2'] %> semester fees for academic year <%= orderData['academic-year'] %> <%= orderData['Reason'] %>. The details of the student(s) are below.
                </p>
                <table class="payment-form__table">
                    <thead class="payment-form__table-header">
                        <tr>
                            <th class="payment-form__table-header-cell">Sl. No</th>
                            <th class="payment-form__table-header-cell">Registration</th>
                            <th class="payment-form__table-header-cell">Names of the student</th>
                            <th class="payment-form__table-header-cell">Payment-date</th>
                            <th class="payment-form__table-header-cell">Amount (Rs.)</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody class="payment-form__table-body">
                        <% orderData.people.forEach((person, index)=> { %>
                            <tr class="payment-form__table-row">
                                <td class="payment-form__table-cell">
                                    <%= index + 1 %>.
                                </td>
                                <td class="payment-form__table-cell">
                                    <%= person.RegistrationNumber %>
                                </td>
                                <td class="payment-form__table-cell">
                                    <%= person.name %>
                                </td>
                                <td class="payment-form__table-cell">
                                    <%= person.Paymentdate %>
                                </td>
                                <td class="payment-form__table-cell">
                                    <%= person.amount %>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                            <% }); %>
                                <tr class="payment-form__table-row">
                                    <td class="payment-form__table-cell"></td>
                                    <td class="payment-form__table-cell1" colspan="3">TOTAL</td>
                                    <td class="payment-form__table-cell">
                                        <%= orderData['\Total Amount'] %>
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
                <p class="payment-form__paragraph1">
                    The student(s) has cleared all the dues till current semester. The fee records of the student(s) have been verified and found that excess registration has been paid. Now, the excess registration fee Rs.<%= orderData['Total Amount'] %>/- (Rupees <%= orderData.amounttowords %> only) has to be refunded. Permission may kindly be accorded to sanction and refund the above amount to the concerned student(s).
                </p>
                <div class="payment-form__paragraph1">
                    <b>Hence it is submitted for approval,</b>
                    <ol class="ordered-list" type="a">
                        <li>
                            Whether the payable amount of Rs.<%= orderData['Total Amount'] %>/- (Rupees <%= orderData.amounttowords %> only) shall be paid to the concerned Student(s) mentioned above.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            Whether the above amount may be paid from IRG NIT Nagaland (Account No.35747839287 / NIT-N Funds (Account No.32201262075 / 10682201001))
                        </li>
                    </ol>
                    <p class="payment-form__approval-text">'a' & 'b' for kind approval please.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="payment-form__approval-sign1">
                    <p class="payment-form__approval-name">(Pappu Kumar Sharma)</p>
                    <p class="payment-form__approval-position">Superintendent (Acad)</p>
                </div>
                <div class="payment-form__approval">   
                    <div class="payment-form__approval-sign">
                        <p class="payment-form__approval-position">Assistant Registrar</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="payment-form__approval-sign">
                        <p class="payment-form__approval-position">Registrar</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="payment-form__approval-sign2">
                    <p class="payment-form__approval-position">Director</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </form>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
